Package: footballdatauk
Type: Package
Title: Read and Clean Football Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Beniamino", "Sartini", email = "sartinibeniamino@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads and downloads football match results and betting odds from
    football-data.co.uk and converts them to a consistent tibble schema.
    The package also includes a small local Italian Serie A example dataset
    for documentation, tests, and offline examples.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/beniamino98/footballdatauk
BugReports: https://github.com/beniamino98/footballdatauk/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    lubridate,
    purrr,
    readr,
    rlang,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    usethis
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
